OL,5,
OL,6,CG1994FAn Afternoon on the Moon airs on
OL,7,FBBC One (CBBC).
OL,8,
OL,9,FPresented by Zoe Ball and Gareth Jones.
OL,10,FMarks the 25th anniversary of man's
OL,11,Ffirst steps on the moon.
OL,12,
OL,13,FGuests: Patrick Moore; Helen Sharman;
OL,14,Fthe second man on the moon, Buzz
OL,15,FAldrin; and making his only CBBC
OL,16,Fappearance, Gilbert the Alien from ITV.
